+## Recovery Proposal Checklist
+
+For the next checkbox-27a worker proposal, the replacement file should be small enough to inspect line by line. It should have this rough shape:
+
+- imports: `json`, `unittest`, and `Path`
+- constants: fixture path and accepted category id set
+- one loader helper for the exact fixture
+- one `_assert_valid_category_records` helper
+- one `_assert_valid_category_record` helper
+- one `unittest.TestCase` with one committed-fixture test
+- `if __name__ == "__main__": unittest.main()`
+
+Do not include mutation helpers in checkbox-27a unless the selected task has advanced to checkbox-27b or later.
